results.name: Decimal expansion of (negative of) Kinkelin constant.
link: G. Almkvist, Asymptotic formulas and generalized Dedekind sums, Exper. Math., 7 (No. 4, 1998), pp. 343-359.
formula: Equals (1 - gamma - log(2*Pi))/12 + Zeta'(2)/(2*Pi^2), where gamma is the Euler-Mascheroni constant A001620. - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Jul 25 2015
results.author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Jun 27 2003
